cc:Work.dc:title: 육십갑자 간지 한국어
cc:Work.dc:description: Diagram depicting the sexagenary cycle (십육갑자), showing, from the inside moving out: the animal (동물), the yin-yang (음양), the earthly branch hangeul (지지), the 지지 hanja, the heavenly stem hanja (천간), the 천간 hangeul, and the element (오행). Derived from https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Chu_K%E1%BB%B3_60_N%C4%83m.svg.
